  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK659">
<l>aḻakkoṇṭa vellā maḻappō miḻappiṉum </l>
<l>piṟpayakku naṟpā lavai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>All that has been obtained with tears (to the victim) will depart with tears (to himself); but what has been by fair means; though with loss at first, will afterwards yield fruit.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
